                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-1025-18380402 t18380402-1025-punishment-99"></join>Transported for Ten Years.</rs>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">LEWIS—
<rs id="t18380402-1025-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
                        <interp inst="t18380402-1025-verdict-2" type="verdictCategory" value="notGuilty"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18380402-1025-verdict-2" type="verdictSubcategory" value=""></interp>NOT GUILTY</rs>
                  </hi>.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183804020108"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Fifth Jury, before Mr. Sergeant Arabin</hi>.</p>
